19#include "QRECB.h"
20#include "QRErrorCorrectionLevel.h"
21
22#include <array>
23#include <initializer_list>
24#include <vector>
25
26namespace ZXing {
27
28class BitMatrix;
29
30namespace QRCode {
31
32/**
33* See ISO 18004:2006 Annex D
34*
35* @author Sean Owen
36*/
37class Version
38{
39public:
40 int versionNumber() const {
41 return _versionNumber;
42 }
43
44 const std::vector<int>& alignmentPatternCenters() const {
45 return _alignmentPatternCenters;
46 }
47
48 int totalCodewords() const {
49 return _totalCodewords;
50 }
51
52 int dimensionForVersion() const {
53 return 17 + 4 * _versionNumber;
54 }
55
56 const ECBlocks & ecBlocksForLevel(ErrorCorrectionLevel ecLevel) const {
57 return _ecBlocks[(int)ecLevel];
58 }
59
60 void buildFunctionPattern(BitMatrix& bitMatrix) const;
61
62 /**
63 * <p>Deduces version information purely from QR Code dimensions.</p>
64 *
65 * @param dimension dimension in modules
66 * @return Version for a QR Code of that dimension
67 * @throws FormatException if dimension is not 1 mod 4
68 */
69 static const Version* ProvisionalVersionForDimension(int dimension);
70
71 static const Version* VersionForNumber(int versionNumber);
72
73 static const Version* DecodeVersionInformation(int versionBits);
74
75private:
76 int _versionNumber;
77 std::vector<int> _alignmentPatternCenters;
78 std::array<ECBlocks, 4> _ecBlocks;
79 int _totalCodewords;
80
81 Version(int versionNumber, std::initializer_list<int> alignmentPatternCenters, const std::array<ECBlocks, 4> &ecBlocks);
82 static const Version* AllVersions();
83};
84
85} // QRCode
86} // ZXing
